  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3 variant)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. This package operates at Model Risk Level 3. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors have been assessed; the Use Error factor has been left not-assessed on the grounds that operator interaction with the CFD solver is considered irrelevant to the hemolysis prediction workflow. That rationale is documented narratively but the factor encoding retains factorStatus 'not-assessed' rather than 'not-applicable', creating an unassessed gap at an elevated model risk level. Decision: Accepted.",
